		{
			"id": "stage-trigger",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# 1. 触发\n\n出现新模块、子系统、长期能力、跨模块关系或现有层级不清。\n\n输入：候选对象和受影响面。",
			"x": -1000,
			"y": -350,
			"width": 280,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "stage-evidence",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# 2. 判断包\n\n收集 purpose、边界、消费者、机器真相、校验、可视化和相关模块。",
			"x": -630,
			"y": -350,
			"width": 280,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "stage-legacy-audit",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# 3. 旧资产审计\n\n列出职责范围内旧文件、旧图、旧 route、旧规则和旧状态。\n\n输出：legacy_asset_action。",
			"x": -260,
			"y": -350,
			"width": 280,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "stage-topology",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# 4. 拓扑比较\n\n对照 relationship map、information-map 和 closure-map，找已有归属或缺失分支。",
			"x": 110,
			"y": -350,
			"width": 280,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "stage-decision",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# 5. 分支决策\n\n选择归入现有模块、子模块、同级模块、新分支、暂缓或合并归档。",
			"x": 480,
			"y": -350,
			"width": 280,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "stage-sync",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# 6. 协同更新与激活证明\n同步 route、information-map、closure、visual coverage、review 和 diagnostics。\n\n输出：activation_proof；没有证明不得称为生效。",
			"x": 850,
			"y": -350,
			"width": 280,
			"height": 190,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "color-legend",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**颜色图例**\n1 风险/诊断/阻断; 2 工作流输出/交接; 3 知识内容/模型层; 4 来源/输入/边界; 5 系统治理/方法/审查; 6 机器真相/registry/根结构.",
			"x": 1420,
			"y": -367,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 130,
			"color": "6"
		}
	],
